---
// Value Proposition component with orange background
---

<section
  class="bg-brand-orange min-h-screen text-white py-24 lg:py-33 xl:py-30"
>
  <div class="max-w-25/32 2xl:max-w-30/32 3xl:max-w-26/32 mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col 2xl:flex-row 2xl:items-center gap-2">
      <!-- Left Content -->
      <div class="flex-1">
        <!-- Subhead -->
        <p
          class="text-sm md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl uppercase text-white mb-4"
          style="line-height: 110%; letter-spacing: 5px;"
        >
          WHAT WE SOLVE
        </p>

        <h2
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-7xl mb-6"
          style="line-height: 120%; font-weight: var(--font-weight-black);"
        >
          We don't just deliver services, we deliver transformative outcomes.
        </h2>

        <p
          class="text-md md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl pb-8"
        >
          Sparq blends strategy, design, engineering, and AI to cut through the
          complexity and create measurable impact, fast.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-md md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl"
        >
          Our approach is modular and adaptive: whether you're building from
          scratch, scaling, or modernizing, we meet you where you are and move
          you where you need to go.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Content - Video -->
      <div class="flex-1 flex 2xl:justify-center">
        <img
          src="/images/videoThumbnail.jpg"
          alt="Product Demo Video"
          class="w-full 2xl:max-w-31/32 h-auto rounded-2xl pt-8 lg:pt-12 xl:pt-16 2xl:pt-8"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Full-width Logo Band -->
  <div class="w-full mt-16 hidden sm:block">
    <img
      src="/images/logo-band.png"
      alt="Partner Logos"
      class="w-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Pull Quote -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-16">
    <p
      class="text-center text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl opacity-80"
      style="font-weight: 400;"
    >
      Reduced mechanical engineering time for a leading manufacturer by over
      95%.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
